attributes.review: Like the blindly faithful disciple to trump I am, I downloaded this app to keep up with what our rapist president is up to nowadays. From the very beginning this app was a distaster...it took 36 months to download and took up all of the storage on my brand new phone. Then, when I finally opened up the app, a photo of an obese orange appeared. It told me to turn on notifications and when I did it charged me 5 million dollars. Next thing you know, Donald Trump smashed through my window in kool-aid man fashion and thanked me for my generous donation. I asked him nicely to leave but next thing you know I was pinned to the floor and he was giving me a spray tan- totally uncalled for😪 So I said “let’s do rock paper scissor” and he said “bet”. He lost and then got so infuriated and called me, I quote, “ a stupid liberal”. I don’t really care what this ass crack of a human thinks so I said “aight bro imma go sleep now” so we did and MAN DOES HE SNORE. No wonder Melania stays 100 feet away from him at all times. At 6am he woke me up and made me order him 25 McMuffins for breakfast. I do not recommend this app please don’t download it.
